## What to expect from our first conversation

When you get in touch, I will ask about your business, your current organic performance, and your goals. I will also take a preliminary look at your site and your competitors before we speak. That way, our first call is productive from the start — I can share initial observations and outline what a realistic engagement would look like.

There is no hard sell. If I do not think SEO is the right channel for your business right now, I will tell you. My reputation depends on delivering results, not on signing retainers.

